name: Experiment Or Die #69
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Transformation is an inevitable byproduct of growing, learning and living. We are not the same person we were 5, 10, 20 years ago because the more we live the more we realize we didn't know anything at all. No matter how old you are if you stop learning, you stop growing, and you might as well stop living! Embrace the change because the world is flying a mile a minute and you better hang on for the ride. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
